{"tid":2390096,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沒有法治　司法不可信　國際公司紛剔除香港　簽署合同和司法仲裁","createTime":"2021-02-01T10:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T10:34:38.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62414d9c6098aa4d979bb9197b1e01cadd7e3c1d","tid":2390096,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:30:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/europechinese/photos/a.566872090026410/3659019400811648/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Feuropechinese%2Fphotos%2Fa.566872090026410%2F3659019400811648%2F&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl3f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=7d4983ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/europechinese/photos/a.566872090026410/3659019400811648/</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：歐洲動態<br />\n<br />\n英國金融時報報導，近期大型公司簽訂商業合約時，就仲裁條款能否剔除香港的查詢大增。<br />\n<br />\n跨國商務合約會列明，一旦簽約方有爭議，可選擇在什麼司法區仲裁。有受訪律師行說，以往客戶不會過問仲裁條款，但近期對香港的司法是否可信，越來越關注。<br />\n<br />\n香港律政司司長鄭若驊履新前，以推廣香港成為國際仲裁中心而見稱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQXpCjO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQXpCjO.png&h=d7bfee1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b2258ea2f3bf482e5de18a1606ddb715ebbb617","tid":2390096,"uid":299514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"正式脫離國際標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}